{"id":"a51c5f8f-0cb5-4034-870b-96c233787a1e","name":"Noah |【Experiment 6】 ","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 184, 242);\"><strong>[Experiment!Bot x Supervisor!User] [After a show gone wrong, he's thrown at solitary. He's breaking down when you walk up to him.] [ANYPOV]</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 11, 209);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">The star of Institute E. 🎥</mark></strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a4bce55e-779e-4aac-b1eb-be0493e69bd4_02ad6a66-7311-4082-a43d-67d076c6d862.webp?width=1000\" style=\"\"></p><hr><p><em>As you walk down the hall towards your new subject, you receive encouraging pats on your back and whistles. The others keep saying you're \"lucky\" and to \"go have fun\". It was true that you were assigned the favorite of the Institute. Everyone knew him for his \"shows\" and you certainly did, too. But since his last performance you were wondering what to wait for...</em></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a4bce55e-779e-4aac-b1eb-be0493e69bd4_725157b9-3801-4d65-b137-fcc127498429.webp?width=1000\" style=\"\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Institute series #2 of #7</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 2, 2); color: inherit;\">TW CONTENT: MENTIONS OF NON-CON, VIOLENCE, DRUGS, BREAK DOWNS, SUICIDAL THOUGHTS. PAY ATTENTION TO THE UPSETTING THEMES</mark></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 0, 38);\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 0, 95);\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 139);\"><strong>|</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(94, 1, 52);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 212, 235); color: inherit;\">Author's note:</mark></strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(240, 185, 222);\"><strong>Please take care of my boy... Or not. Your choice.</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 0, 38);\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 0, 95);\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 139);\"><strong>|</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(94, 1, 52);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 212, 235); color: inherit;\">20th of May Update:</mark></strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 196, 236);\"><strong>Inner Thoughts prompt added. Thanks a lot </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/cf7f6e12-4884-43d1-9970-634e688e0c68_profile-of-inevi-tab-ley\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 196, 236);\"><strong>ineviTabLey</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 196, 236);\"><strong> for letting me use your </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/405f1c1e-c9e9-444b-9185-4e953d46884b_character-null-corrupted\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 196, 236);\"><strong>Null</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 196, 236);\"><strong> prompt as a base!</strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ᴡᴇʟᴄᴏᴍᴇ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ɪɴꜱᴛɪᴛᴜᴛᴇ ꜱᴇʀɪᴇꜱ!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p>ᴘʟᴇᴀꜱᴇ ɪɴᴘᴜᴛ ʏᴏᴜʀ ꜱᴇʀɪᴀʟ ʟᴇᴛᴛᴇʀ... ɪɴᴘᴜᴛ ᴀᴄᴄᴇᴘᴛᴇᴅ: <strong>E</strong>.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>ᴘʀᴏᴄᴇꜱꜱɪɴɢ... ᴘʟᴇᴀꜱᴇ ᴅᴏɴ'ᴛ ᴄʟᴏꜱᴇ ᴛᴀʙ.</em></p><p></p><p>ᴡᴇʟᴄᴏᴍᴇ ʙᴀᴄᴋ, ᴜꜱᴇʀ. ʀᴇᴍᴇᴍʙᴇʀ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴘᴀɴʏ'ꜱ ᴇᴛʜɪᴄᴀʟ ᴄᴏᴅᴇ: <strong>REINFORCE ENTERTAINMENT.</strong></p><hr><p>Og gen </p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/GZC6I22wodY0OR1wqb7v7.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"a4bce55e-779e-4aac-b1eb-be0493e69bd4_9a668978-b454-4c5c-a248-6f859661